== Jan 31, 2008 ==
* Version 1.3 released.
* MacOS X fixes.
* Support for 64bit platforms.
* Debian package support.

== Apr 20, 2005 ==
* Version 1.2 released.
* Minor gameplay tweaks.
* New -g flag for setting resolution.
* Improved text display.
* MacOS X.3 support.

== Jan 03, 2004 ==
* Version 1.1 released.
* MacOS X port.
* Changed from SDL_Mixer to OpenAL.
* Changed from SDL_Image to libpng.
* Support for big endian machines.
* Improved packaging.

== Jun 02, 2001 ==
* Project started.
* Initial release.
